description: Cint AB is a Sweden-based company active in the software sector. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm.  The firm produces and sells online market research products for businesses, organizations and individuals involved in market research; notably researchers, survey tool providers, planners, marketing professionals, entrepreneurs, panel providers, publishers and non-profit organizations. The company specializes in software as a service (SaaS, web-based software solutions offering online sample management and access, as well as online panel management products that are accessible worldwide. Its business portfolio comprises products such as Cint Access, Cint Link, Cint Engage, Cint Optimizer, and OpinionHUB, among others. The company has offices in Europe, North America and Asia-Pacific. Its investors include Prime Technology Ventures NV and Creandum AB.
